html2text: html2text (converts HTML documents into plain text)
html2text:
html2text: html2text is a command line utility, written in C++,
html2text: that converts HTML documents into plain text. Each
html2text: HTML document is loaded from a location indicated by
html2text: a URI or read from standard input, and formatted into
html2text: a stream of plain text characters that is written to
html2text: standard output or into an output-file. The input-URI
html2text: may specify a remote site, from that the documents
html2text: are loaded via the Hypertext Transfer Protocol (HTTP).
html2text:
